The paper proposes a distributed computing scheme based on coding theory to address the straggler problem. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
